{
  "stem": "15962.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I think we were keenly aware that how dangerous it was to, to eat anything we, we put our hands on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And indeed, many, many people died within the next hours because their system just couldn't take any food, any normal food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "None, none of us, as to the best of my knowledge, succumbed to that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I should also say that as we were walking to this village, we saw a profusion of American troops.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And what stands out vividly in my mind, if anything is vivid at all, is a long row of huge tanks with black troops sitting on top of them and throwing us bars of chocolate.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And indeed, only a few years ago, it was shown that there were, there was a black tank battalion that was-- at one point, erroneously, thought that they'd liberated Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a big affair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had to actually withdraw the film.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they were in Gunskirchen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't liberate the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they were troops that fought nearby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We must have been quite a sight, dragging ourselves from the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We spent the night near this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] warehouse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the next day--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just on the outside somewhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next day, I believe that they told us to walk towards a larger city called Wels.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And shortly after we got on the road, some Belgian troops helped us, put us on their truck, and drove us to a little place called Horsching, which was a huge Luftwaffe and German Air Force base, military base, near the town of Wels, which is, I think, the second-largest town in Austria.",
      "word_count": 53
    }
  ],
